{"tid":85426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好人好事】銀行提款過年被搶,熱心途人合力擒賊","createTime":"2017-01-18T10:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T10:51:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7bcbd70c9f2ea6b3e24e53ed12feb8fc7d079627","tid":85426,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/7izv1j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F7izv1j.jpg&h=cef2c702&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/7xvDO1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F7xvDO1.jpg&h=0f7e5184&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早上11時15分，72歲姓梁老翁，在葵涌石宜路的中國銀行提取7萬元後，攜著該袋現鈔途至附近社區會堂對開，突被一名賊人從後搶去其袋。事主大聲呼叫，驚動兩名熱心途人協助追截。 <br />\n<br />\n賊匪直奔往約200米外，大隴街的順豐速遞門市，適時一名隸屬九龍城軍裝巡邏小隊的休班警車車長「七星」，剛巧在內處理私務，得悉事件步出攔截；賊匪頓時慌不擇路原路折返，最終在社區會堂附近被眾人抓到，由於賊人孔武有力，「七星」與途人合力將43歲姓周賊人按地制服。「七星」在與賊人糾纏期間，亦有受傷。 <br />\n<br />\n讀者吳先生當時行經上址，見至少4名警員押著疑犯上警車，遇劫男事主則在場協助調查，警員詢問梁伯有否高血壓及心臟病，梁伯表示起初「好驚」，現心情已有所平復。吳先生相信，有關賊匪覷準臨近農曆新年，有長者會往銀行提錢時伺機落手，加上上址較多斜路，長者較難追賊，幸今次有熱心途人「幫到手」。<br />\n麥芽酥 +  引用 18/1/2017 17:30<br />\n有片: <a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170118&amp;guid=56188130&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170118%26guid%3D56188130%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=16198e04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170118%26guid%3D56188130%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=d288ca97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170118&amp;guid=56188130&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"b3c1e758ab57b001fc6a8d6cd19a65d27128b705","tid":85426,"uid":19933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2